{title: Directive Selectors}

{textfont-guitar: Courier}
{textfont-piano: Helvetica}
{textsize-guitar: 10}
{textsize-piano: 12}
{chordcolour-guitar: darkblue}
{chordcolour-piano: darkgreen}

{comment: Selectors allow instrument-specific or user-specific formatting}

{chordfont-user-beginner: Arial Bold}
{chordsize-user-beginner: 16}
{textfont-user-advanced: Times}
{textsize-user-advanced: 9}

{start_of_verse}
[G]Selectors let you [C]customize
[D]Per instrument or [G]user
[Em]Guitar sees [C]Courier
[D]Piano sees Helve[G]tica
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[C]Different [G]views
[D]Same [Em]song
[C]Everyone [G]gets
[D]What they want [G]along
{end_of_chorus}
